{"tid":1871071,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有關情緒問題 (理大)","createTime":"2020-02-09T08:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T09:38:21.000Z","uid":254946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad8e145af54480b66f46eb83417001f192a3dc0","tid":1871071,"uid":254946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"PolyU應用社會科學系以下有一所輔導中心的，如果大家/識人有需要用到輔導服務，可以考慮。每次只需50大元。<br />\n<br />\n網上申請就可以了：  <a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/pfs/index.php/712859?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fpfs%2Findex.php%2F712859%3Flang%3Den&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfquoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=63d43c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/pfs/index.php/712859?lang=en</a>  <br />\n<br />\n服務是由修讀 *諮商與輔導碩士 的受訓輔導員提供，他們都已修讀有關的科目，並由資深導師及教授直接督導*，保證服務專業。<br />\n<br />\n輔導一節約45-50分鐘的面談，在polyu進行。時間可選星期一至五，晚上6:30-8:30或星前六早上10:00-12:00。詳情可參考單張。"},{"pid":"c17a58b58102449767ada4068042f645d751403a","tid":1871071,"uid":208280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔係poly人用到嗎"},{"pid":"baf4a6face31eba22bef02334f0af2cfe004e667","tid":1871071,"uid":254946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17a58b58102449767ada4068042f645d751403a","tid":1871071,"uid":208280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔係poly人用到嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"一樣會收街客~!!"}]}